quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  3,52,"“Koma pamene Isa (Yesu) adazindikira mwa iwo kusakhulupirira adati: “Ndani akhale athandizi anga kwa Allah (popitiriza kufalitsa Chipembedzo Chake)?” Ophunzira ake adati: “Ife ndife athandizi a Allah (pofalitsa Chipembedzo Chake). Takhulupirira Allah; ndipo ikira umboni kuti ife ndithu ndi odzipereka kwa Allah (Asilamu).”"
  3,53,"““Mbuye wathu! Tazikhulupirira zimene mwavumbulutsa, ndipo tamtsata Mtumikiyo. Choncho tilembeni pamodzi ndi oikira umboniwo.”"
  3,54,"“Ndipo (Ayuda) adakonza chiwembu (chofuna kupha Isa (Yesu), koma Allah adachiwononga chiwembu chawocho. Allah Ngokhoza bwino zedi poononga ziwembu za anthu a chiwembu"
  3,55,"“(Kumbukirani) pamene Allah adati: “Iwe Isa (Yesu)! Ine ndikukwaniritsira nyengo yako yokhala ndi moyo (Ayuda sachita kanthu kwa iwe). Ndipo ndikunyamulira kwa Ine ndiponso ndikuyeretsa kwa anthu osakhulupirira (omwe ndi adani ako). Ndipo amene akutsata (iwe) ndiwasankha kukhala apamwamba pa amene sadakhulupirire kufikira tsiku lachimaliziro. Kenako kobwerera kwanu nkwa Ine, ndipo ndidzaweruza pakati panu pa zomwe mudali kusiyana"
  3,56,"“Tsono amene sadakhulupirire, ndiwakhaulitsa ndi chilango chaukali pa dziko lapansi ndi tsiku lachimaliziro, ndipo sadzapeza athandizi"
  3,57,"“Koma amene akhulupirira nachita zabwino, (Allah) adzawalipira malipiro awo (mokwanira). Ndipo Allah sakonda anthu ochita zoipa"
  3,58,“Izi tikukuwerengera iwezi ndi zivumbulutso ndi ulaliki waluntha
  3,59,"“Ndithudi, fanizo la Isa (Yesu) kwa Allah lili ngati fanizo la Adam; adamulenga ndi dothi namuuza kuti: “Khala munthu.” Ndipo adakhaladi"
  3,60,“(Ichi ndi) choona chochokera kwa Mbuye wako; choncho usakhale mwa okaikira
  3,61,"“Tsopano amene akutsutsana nawe (iwe Mtumiki s.a.w) pa ichi pambuyo pokudzera kuzindikira, auze: “Bwerani tiitane ana athu ndi ana anu, akazi athu ndi akazi anu, ife ndi inu; kenako modzichepetsa tipemphe tembelero la Allah kuti likhale pa amene ali abodza (mwa ife).”"
  3,62,"“Ndithu iyi ndinkhani yoona; ndipo palibe woyenera kupembedzedwa mwa choonadi koma Allah. Ndithudi, Iye Allah Ngwamphamvu Zoposa, Ngwanzeru Zakuya"
  3,63,"“Ngati atembenuka (monyoza, Allah awalanga); ndithudi Allah Ngodziwa za oononga"
  3,64,"“Nena: “Inu eni buku (la Allah, Ayuda ndi Akhrisitu!) Idzani ku liwu lolingana pakati pathu ndi inu (lakuti) tisapembedze aliyense koma Allah (Mmodzi Yekha), ndiponso tisamphatikize ndi chilichonse ndipo ena mwa ife asawasandutse anzawo kukhala milungu m’malo mwa Allah.” Ngati atembenuka ndi kunyoza, nenani: “Ikirani umboni kuti ife ndife Asilamu (ogonjera malamulo a Allah).”"
  3,65,“E inu amene mwapatsidwa buku! Bwanji mukutsutsana za Ibrahim pomwe Taurat ndi Injili sizidavumbulutsidwe koma pambuyo pake. Kodi simuzindikira
  3,66,"“Taonani! Inu mudatsutsana pa zomwe mudazidziwa, nanga bwanji mukutsutsana pa zomwe simuzidziwa? Allah ndi Yemwe akudziwa. Pomwe inu simudziwa"
  3,67,"“Ibrahim sadali Myuda ndipo sadali Mkhrisitu, koma adali wolungama Msilamu (wodzipereka); ndipo sadali mwa ophatikiza (Allah ndi zinthu zina)"
  3,68,"“Ndithu anthu omwe ali oyenera kudzilumikiza ndi Ibrahim ndi amene adamutsata (m’nyengo yake) ndi Mtumiki uyu (Muhammad {s.a.w}) ndi amene amkhulupirira (Mtumikiyu). Ndipo Allah ndi Mtetezi wa okhulupirira"
  3,69,"“Gulu lina la anthu amene adapatsidwa buku likufuna kukusokeretsani; ndipo sasokeretsa aliyense koma iwo wokha, pomwe (iwo eni) sakuzindikira"
  3,70,“E inu amene mwapatsidwa buku! Bwanji mukuzikana zizindikiro za Allah (Qur’an) pomwe mukudziwa
  3,71,"“E inu amene mwapatsidwa buku! Bwanji mukusakaniza choona ndi chabodza, ndipo mukubisa choona uku mukudziwa"
  3,72,"“Ndipo gulu lina la amene adapatsidwa buku lidati (kwa anzawo): “Khulupirirani chomwe chavumbulutsidwa kwa Asilamu kumayambiliro kwa usana, ndipo chikaneni kumalekezero kwake (kwa usana) mwina angabwelere (kusiya Chisilamu)"
  3,73,"“Ndipo musakhulupirire aliyense kupatula yekhayo yemwe watsata chipembedzo chanu. (Allah adauza Mtumiki {s.a.w}), nena: “Ndithudi, chiongoko chenicheni ndi chiongoko cha Allah basi.” (Amene adapatsidwa buku Adanena kwa anzawo: “Musakhulupirire) kuti angapatsidwe aliyense zofanana ndi zomwe mwapatsidwa inu (Ayuda ndi Akhrisitu), kapena kuti angakutsutseni kwa Mbuye wanu.” (Allah adati kwa mtumiki{s.a.w}), nena: “Ndithu zabwino zonse zili m’manja mwa Allah; amazipereka kwa yemwe wamfuna. Allah ndi Mataya, Ngodziwa.”"
  3,74,“Amamsankhira chifundo Chake amene wamfuna. Ndipo Allah ndi Mwini ubwino wawukulu